      <title>交易商押注南非将比预期更快降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/traders-revise-south-africa-rate-cut-bets-as-credit-growth-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在流入经济的资金量和私营部门贷款录得近两年来最弱增长后，交易员将南非首次降息的押注提前至 2024 年 3 月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/traders-revise-south-africa-rate-cut-bets-as-credit-growth-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
