    <item>
      <title>7万亿美元的ETF繁荣再次因愚蠢的股票走势而受到指责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/the-7-trillion-etf-boom-gets-blamed-again-for-dumb-stock-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是对被动投资热潮的最新批评：新的学术研究声称，华尔街追逐指数的资金源源不断地涌入，正在扭曲股价并引发极端的市场波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/the-7-trillion-etf-boom-gets-blamed-again-for-dumb-stock-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经合组织认为发达经济体经济放缓加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-11-29/oecd-sees-a-deepening-slowdown-in-advanced-economies-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织的最新预测显示，全球发达经济体的经济放缓将在 2024 年进一步加剧，继 2023 年增长 2.9% 后，明年全球国内生产总值 (GDP) 预计将仅增长 2.7%。经合组织首席经济学家克莱尔·隆巴德利 (Clare Lombardelli) 解释了这一结果。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-11-29/oecd-sees-a-deepening-slowdown-in-advanced-economies-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:08:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
