      <title>英国对 Elliott 作出裁决，LME 赢得镍危机诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/lme-wins-nickel-crisis-case-as-uk-rules-against-elliott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所赢得了埃利奥特投资管理公司(Elliott Investment Management)在英国法院提起的诉讼，该诉讼因其有争议的决定停止去年镍市场失控的空头挤压，消除了伦敦金属交易所在寻求摆脱危机时面临的最大威胁之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/lme-wins-nickel-crisis-case-as-uk-rules-against-elliott</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:04:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
